      "description": "The Innovator U.S. Small Cap Power Buffer ETF - December (KDEC) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in downside hedge alternatives. The fund aims to participate in the price movement of the iShares Russell 2000 ETF, up to a predetermined cap, while buffering the first 15% of losses over a one-year period. The fund is actively managed, using FLEX options and collateral to provide exposure KDEC was launched on Nov 29, 2024 and is issued by Innovator.",
